{"tid":1955214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「天水園人」沙嶺公墓的亡魂","createTime":"2020-04-02T10:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T05:27:11.000Z","uid":211906,"like":66,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"fe2d4c93ea91f5bbf6d04f64f77d7a7a53de4577","tid":1955214,"uid":211906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"梁錦祥：忘記這段歷史，就是對不起已經犧牲了的手足。因此，我要提醒大家，港人永遠都不要忘記葬在沙嶺公墓的英靈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/03/31/editor/梁錦祥：沙嶺公墓/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmaddog.myradio.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F31%2Feditor%2F%E6%A2%81%E9%8C%A6%E7%A5%A5%EF%BC%9A%E6%B2%99%E5%B6%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%A2%93%2F&d=M80n4YL9TfmCcvG0giRsMnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=dfa23058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://maddog.myradio.hk/2020/03/31/editor/梁錦祥：沙嶺公墓/</a><br />\n <br />\n雖然我唔知道入面有幾多個係手足 但如果有一個係 我都想去悼念佢<br />\n<br />\n我希望可以做多少少 聽日我會係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍銀座空地 夜晚8點 黃雨嬲記認</span></span>  收集各位心意 可能係一封信或者零食或者你覺得有意義既物件 後日代大家帶去沙嶺<br />\n<br />\n我唔知咁做係咪好無謂好冇意義 但我唔做個心唔舒服 <br />\n<br />\n希望各位有時間都可以去拜祭 最好係自己地區學我咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"b4751989ce374855323ddc4e3b9ebe24e2761563","tid":1955214,"uid":33786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81200462da42654f309649a347a1c4501fe9b738","tid":1955214,"uid":84968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99982f158cce289fc6970258afaac766da8592a3","tid":1955214,"uid":297981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T10:52:56.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmo